# 💊 Medical Reminder App

A simple and elegant React-based frontend app to help users remember their daily medications on time. Designed with Bootstrap for responsive UI and clean user experience. Ideal for beginners in full-stack development.

---
## 🚀 Live Demo

Try it out:  
👉 [https://esvinth.netlify.app/)

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Add medicine reminders
- ⏰ Set specific reminder time
- 📋 View all reminders in card layout
- ✔️ Mark medicines as taken
- 🔧 Modular component structure
- 📱 Fully responsive design using Bootstrap

---

